# SkyGuard Frontend - Professional UI/UX Guidelines

## Design Philosophy
- **Professional Enterprise UI**: Clean, minimal, and functional design suitable for business applications
- **No Flashy Elements**: Avoid gradients, excessive animations, or amateur-looking effects
- **Consistent Typography**: Use clear hierarchy with professional font weights and sizes
- **Subtle Color Palette**: Primarily grays, whites, and minimal accent colors
- **Clean Spacing**: Consistent margins, padding, and layout grids

## Color System
- **Primary**: Use subtle blues (#475569, #64748b) for accents only
- **Background**: White (#ffffff) and light grays (#f8fafc, #f1f5f9)
- **Text**: Dark grays (#0f172a, #334155, #64748b) for hierarchy
- **Borders**: Light grays (#e2e8f0, #cbd5e1)
- **Success**: Subtle green (#059669)
- **Warning**: Subtle amber (#d97706)
- **Error**: Subtle red (#dc2626)

## Typography
- **Headings**: Inter font, weights 600-700, clean hierarchy
- **Body**: Inter font, weight 400-500, 14-16px base size
- **Labels**: Inter font, weight 500, 12-14px
- **No decorative fonts or excessive text effects**

## Layout Principles
- **Sidebar Navigation**: Use vertical sidebar instead of horizontal tabs
- **Grid System**: 8px base unit for spacing consistency
- **Cards**: Clean white backgrounds with subtle shadows
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first approach with clean breakpoints

## Component Standards
- **Buttons**: Clean, minimal with subtle hover states
- **Cards**: White background, subtle border or shadow
- **Tables**: Clean rows with proper spacing and typography
- **Forms**: Clear labels, proper spacing, minimal styling
- **Navigation**: Clean sidebar with professional icons

## What NOT to Use
- ❌ Gradient backgrounds (cosmic, aurora, rainbow effects)
- ❌ Excessive animations or transitions
- ❌ Bright, flashy colors
- ❌ Oversized typography or decorative fonts
- ❌ Complex visual effects or glassmorphism
- ❌ Amateur-looking design patterns
- ❌ Horizontal tab navigation for main app sections

## Professional Patterns
- ✅ Clean sidebar navigation with icons
- ✅ Subtle hover states and interactions
- ✅ Consistent spacing and typography
- ✅ Professional color scheme
- ✅ Clear visual hierarchy
- ✅ Minimal, functional design
- ✅ Enterprise-grade appearance

## Code Standards
- Use Tailwind utility classes for consistency
- Keep components clean and focused
- Avoid inline styles
- Use semantic HTML structure
- Ensure accessibility standards
- Maintain responsive design patterns

## Dashboard Specific
- **Layout**: Sidebar + main content area
- **Navigation**: Vertical menu with clear sections
- **Content**: Clean cards with subtle shadows
- **Charts**: Professional styling with muted colors
- **Status**: Clean indicators without flashy effects

Remember: This is professional weather intelligence software for enterprise clients, not a flashy consumer app. Keep it clean, functional, and trustworthy.